<section class="hero topo-bg" style="padding-bottom:48px;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="label">Free Quote</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3.4rem);">Tell us what<br>you need covered.</h1>
    <p style="max-width:520px; margin-top:16px; font-size:1.05rem;">We'll come back with real options from real carriers — not a placeholder estimate.</p>
  </div>
